```json
{
  "header": {
    "analysis_summary": "画面拥有绝佳的侧向暖色光影和生动的人物表情，但左右两侧元素较杂乱（左侧被切断的人物和右侧巨大的遮阳伞遮挡了视觉重心）。长投影是极具表现力的艺术元素，应当被更好地强调。"
  },
  "compositions": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title_cn": "暖阳下的生动人像",
      "image_gen_prompt": "Medium portrait of a smiling elderly man in a blue shirt standing against a sunlit grey wall, dramatic long shadow, golden hour lighting, cinematic street photography.",
      "instruction_steps": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "action": "ZOOM",
          "direction": "In",
          "magnitude_val": 2.2,
          "magnitude_unit": "x",
          "text_cn": "放大画面至 2.2 倍，剔除左右干扰者，专注于中心人物的笑容"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "action": "SHIFT",
          "direction": "Right",
          "magnitude_val": 0.5,
          "magnitude_unit": "meters",
          "text_cn": "向右移动半步，调整构图使人物与影子形成平衡的三角结构"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "action": "VIEW",
          "direction": "Tilt-down",
          "magnitude_val": 5.0,
          "magnitude_unit": "degrees",
          "text_cn": "镜头略微向下倾斜，压低背景墙的留白，使画面更有沉浸感"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title_cn": "光影叙事极简构图",
      "image_gen_prompt": "A street photo of market vendors and their very long shadows on a plain wall, minimalist composition, silhouette-like shadows, high contrast sunlight.",
      "instruction_steps": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "action": "SHIFT",
          "direction": "Left",
          "magnitude_val": 3.0,
          "magnitude_unit": "steps",
          "text_cn": "向左走约 3 步，避开右侧遮阳伞的干扰，将画面视角拉开"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "action": "ZOOM",
          "direction": "In",
          "magnitude_val": 1.2,
          "magnitude_unit": "x",
          "text_cn": "微调焦距至 1.2 倍，确保墙面占据画面主体，强调影子的延展感"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "action": "VIEW",
          "direction": "Tilt-up",
          "magnitude_val": 10.0,
          "magnitude_unit": "degrees",
          "text_cn": "采用略微仰拍视角，增加人物的视觉高度，并使地面上的农产品作为前景点缀"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

```json
{
  "header": {
    "analysis_summary": "画面拥有极佳的午后侧逆光，形成的拉长阴影具有强烈的叙事感。但左侧路人干扰了主体视线，构图略显散乱，且地平线有轻微倾斜。"
  },
  "compositions": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title_cn": "温暖瞬间人像特写",
      "image_gen_prompt": "Cinematic portrait of a smiling elderly man in a blue shirt, golden hour sunlight, sharp shadows on a concrete wall, shallow depth of field, street photography style.",
      "instruction_steps": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "action": "SHIFT",
          "direction": "Right",
          "magnitude_val": 2.0,
          "magnitude_unit": "meters",
          "text_cn": "向右移动约 2 米，将左侧提水壶的人移除出画面"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "action": "ZOOM",
          "direction": "In",
          "magnitude_val": 2.0,
          "magnitude_unit": "x",
          "text_cn": "放大画面至 2 倍焦距，聚焦老人的神态与伞下的互动"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "action": "VIEW",
          "direction": "Tilt-down",
          "magnitude_val": 5.0,
          "magnitude_unit": "degrees",
          "text_cn": "镜头向下微倾，将地面的蔬菜摊作为前景引导"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title_cn": "光影几何叙事",
      "image_gen_prompt": "Wide angle street photography, long shadows of people cast on a grey wall at sunset, minimalist composition, graphic play of light and shadow, urban life scene.",
      "instruction_steps": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "action": "SHIFT",
          "direction": "Left",
          "magnitude_val": 2.0,
          "magnitude_unit": "steps",
          "text_cn": "向左横移约 2 步，使雨伞的阴影与老人身体分开，增强光影美感"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "action": "ZOOM",
          "direction": "In",
          "magnitude_val": 1.2,
          "magnitude_unit": "x",
          "text_cn": "稍微拉近，精准裁剪掉最左侧的杂乱物体"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "action": "VIEW",
          "direction": "Tilt-adjust",
          "magnitude_val": 3.0,
          "magnitude_unit": "degrees",
          "text_cn": "向右旋转手机约 3 度，矫正地面水平线"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

```json
{
  "header": {
    "analysis_summary": "金色的夕阳光线在墙上投射出极具戏剧性的长阴影，但画面右侧人物背影过于遮挡视线，且左侧构图略显散乱，缺乏明确的视觉中心。"
  },
  "compositions": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title_cn": "金秋暖阳人像特写",
      "image_gen_prompt": "A close-up street portrait of a smiling elderly man in a light blue polo shirt, bathed in warm golden hour sunlight, long dramatic shadows on a plain concrete wall behind him, cinematic lighting, sharp focus on eyes.",
      "instruction_steps": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "action": "ZOOM",
          "direction": "In",
          "magnitude_val": 2.5,
          "magnitude_unit": "x",
          "text_cn": "放大画面至 2.5 倍，排除右侧遮挡物，聚焦中心男子的生动表情"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "action": "SHIFT",
          "direction": "Right",
          "magnitude_val": 0.5,
          "magnitude_unit": "meters",
          "text_cn": "向右平移约 0.5 米，使人物处于画面三分线位置，并与墙上的阴影形成呼应"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "action": "VIEW",
          "direction": "Tilt-down",
          "magnitude_val": 5,
          "magnitude_unit": "degrees",
          "text_cn": "手机向下微俯 5 度，避开顶部过亮区域，使光影更有层次感"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title_cn": "光影叙事极简构图",
      "image_gen_prompt": "Cinematic wide shot of a man standing against a grey wall, long silhouette shadows stretched across the wall during golden hour, minimalist composition, street photography style.",
      "instruction_steps": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "action": "SHIFT",
          "direction": "Left",
          "magnitude_val": 2,
          "magnitude_unit": "steps",
          "text_cn": "向左跨 2 步，寻找一个可以避开右侧人物的角度，让画面更简洁"
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "action": "ZOOM",
          "direction": "In",
          "magnitude_val": 1.2,
          "magnitude_unit": "x",
          "text_cn": "稍微放大画面至 1.2 倍，裁掉底部零乱的地面杂物"
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "action": "VIEW",
          "direction": "Tilt-up",
          "magnitude_val": 10,
          "magnitude_unit": "degrees",
          "text_cn": "将手机向上抬起 10 度，增加上方墙面的留白，利用光影留出故事感空间"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
